  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] From there, we were sent to-- I was sent to Hanover, in an area of Hanover that was called Linden-Limmer.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "L-I-N-D-E-N capital L-I-M-M-E-R.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Linden-Limmer.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "There was a huge factory called the Continental Gummi Werke.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Continental-- Gummi, G-U-M-M-I-- Werke-- W-E-R-K-E, which means the Continental Rubber Factory.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I performed slave labor at the Continental Gummi Werke, at the age of 15.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "My job was to-- to-- well, we worked on an assembly line there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And we worked on gas masks.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Hitler wanted all his subjects to have a gas mask, fearing poison gas attacks by the allies-- which, however, never materialized.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] As a result of that, he decided to save a few of us and put us into the-- his factories throughout Germany.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I-- now, there was another reason, of course, and for different purposes.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "The men of Germany were in the service, and the factories needed to be run.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And so we were distributed into all these factories in different places, doing different things.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "So I will describe to you what I did in-- in Hanover and so forth, in the-- in the-- in the future camps.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "On this assembly-- this assembly line kept moving, and each of us to perform a different function on a gas mask.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And if we could not finish our function in-- of that gas mask, we were to take it and just drop it by our side.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Now-- and all of us had found ourselves in a situation that we could not finish it.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "They could adjust that belt different-- at different speed, and so sometimes it went so fast that one-- it was impossible for us to even touch it.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "So sometimes we had to just drop it.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
